column5: Is it 1986?  Jets Flyers game is 8-8 with time left in the 3rd!!!  tsn said it's the first 16 goal game since the lock-out.
what a wild game! I was blown away when it was 5-1 jets! let alone 9-8 This won't do any good for the goalies GAA.

Time warp? You want time warp? I lived in a house in the mid 60's for about a year ...95 Chester Avenue in Toronto. The rent was $125. a month. I could have bought it for $12,000.00 Well, this morning early I was surfing and checked out where I've lived in the past....not many places. The place looks decent enough on Google maps. Well the house about 4 doors away is presently for sale for a million dollars! DANG!
buy it now for a million and it should be worth 83 000 000 in 50 years.
Can't buy'er now, Chad. My fixed income is broken.
I watched the high-lights on TSN this morning. They just played the game and didn't say a word.... just... SCores.... SCORES... SCORES ... SCORes.... SCORes. .hahahah
3-1, 3-3, 3-4.  The scores by period.  ... and then a baseball game that neither team seemed to want to win.
